Existem erros com datas de no factveis nos dados, para simplifio

In [11]:
def getDays(td):
    d = td.days
    if 0 <= d <= 30:
        return d
    elif d < 0 and -d <= 30:
        return -d
    return 30
        
df["dataDiff"] = df["dataNotificacao"] - df["dataInicioSintomas"]
diff = df["dataDiff"].apply(getDays)
